	(text "warning:\nULX3S has different pinout\nfor simpler PCB routing and\nbecause FT230X has weak CTS\ndrive capability. (Undocumented,\nFLEAfpga mail from 13-Nov-2015)\nULX2S pinout was:\nTCK = DSR\nTMS = RI\nTDI = CTS\nTDO = DCD\n"
